{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "夜雨漓漓，谭门三霸天赶到平安老店，发现王风对着一口棳材喝酒。谭天虎力力要踢踢棳材，却被神秘力量击碎膝盖。谭天龙出手时亦遭同样命运。王风发现地上有四块血红色小石头，每块都能打断一条腿，还能夺去人的魂魄。谭天龙临死前将一颗价值连城的明珠送给王风，并指着窗外的空鹦鹉笼，伺佛要说出鹦鹉的秘密，却已气绝。老掌柜告诉王风，鹦鹉叫小魔神，是一位叫血奴的女人送给他的，只可怕在七月初一鬼门开之夜被吓死。血奴在前面巷子里的鹦鹉楼，而鹦鹉就是血鹦鹉的奴才。王风决定前往鹦鹉楼探索真相。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "这里是酒店？还是棳材铺？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "掌柜的",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "text": "小店只卖酒，不卖棳材。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "酒店里怎能会有棳材？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "掌柜的",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "text": "那是这位客官带来的，而且一定要带到屋里来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "掌柜的",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "text": "因为这位客官一定要棳材里朋友陪他喝酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这杯酒轮到我了，我喝。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这是你带来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "text": "有个朋友。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "是死朋友？还是活朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "text": "只要是朋友，死活都一样是朋友。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "死人也会喝酒？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这杯酒轮到你了，我替你喝。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_long",
      "text": "原来这小子是个酒鬼。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_long",
      "speaker_name": "谭天龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "text": "叫他快把棳材搬出去，叫他的人也滚出去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "小子，你听见没有？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "text": "听见什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "大爷们叫你把棳材搬出去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "text": "搬不得。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "text": "外面在下雨，我不能让我的朋友淋雨。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这人是疯子，你看怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_long",
      "speaker_name": "谭天龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "text": "踢出去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_long",
      "text": "踢疯子不犯法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_long",
      "speaker_name": "谭天龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "text": "踢死人更不犯法。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_long",
      "text": "好，那我就先踢死人，再踢疯子。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "text": "我这朋友活着的时候一向只喜欢踢人，从来也没有被人踢过，死了也一定不喜欢被人踢的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_hu",
      "speaker_name": "谭天虎",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "行！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_long",
      "speaker_name": "谭天龙",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这是什么功夫？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_long",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_long",
      "speaker_name": "谭天龙",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "出手的不是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_tian_long",
      "speaker_name": "谭天龙",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "不是你是谁。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_tian_tian_long",
      "text": "也许根本不是人。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你看见了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我什么都没看见。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "我说过，出手的不是我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "像大爷这种功夫，我连做梦都没有看见过。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你看这是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "好像是块石头，红石头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "这样的石头，地上一定还有三块。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "嘟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "四块石头，打断了四条腿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这么样一块小石头，也能打断人的腿？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你不信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "这种事我本来也不信，却偏偏让我凑巧看见了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这…这是武功？还是魔法？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "我也不知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这是谁打出来的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "我本来怀疑是你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "不是我，绝不是。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "现在我也知道不是了，石头是从窗子外面打进来的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "外面那鸟笼是你的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "是只鹦鹉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "它是怎么死的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "它死得很奇怪，看来就好像是被吓死的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "吓死的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "那天晚上，我本来已经睡了，忽然听见它在叫，就好像……就好像一个人在害怕时发出的那种惊呼一样。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "等到我赶出来时，它已经死了，死得好惨。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "那是什么时候的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我记得很清楚，那天晚上是七月初一。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "因为那天正好是开鬼门关的日子，晚上我还祭过鬼神，还喝了点酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我知道你心里在想什么。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "嘟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "鬼门关开了，冤魂野鬼都出来了，到了人间……你心里一定在想，我的小魔神，也是被鬼吓死的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "小魔神？你那只鹦鹉，叫小魔神？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你为什么会替它取个这种名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这名字不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "我只不过奇怪……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "其实这名字也不是我取的，是她……她把鹦鹉送给我的时候，鹦鹉就已经有了这名字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "她是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我这一辈子，都是在规规矩矩的做人，可是我也曽荒唐过一次。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "她实在是了不起的女人，有时可爱得要命，有时又可怕得要命。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "所以你宁愿将一生的积蓄都送给她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我一点都不后悔。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "如果老天还让我能再活十年，再让我存那么多钱，我一定还会再到她那里去一次。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "她那里究竟是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你听见也许会觉得很可笑，那里只不过是个姓院。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "虽然她只不过是个姓女，是个婢子，但我却随时都愿意跪在地上，去舔她的脚。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "那姓院叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "叫鹦鹉楼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "她叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
